title: Cosmic Queries: Space Probes with Dr. Amy Mainzer
description: JPL astrophysicist Dr. Amy Mainzer is back as guest host for this week’s podcast, and together with comic co-host Chuck Nice she answers your questions about space probes.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
